Industry Policy Task Force
Kick-Off Meeting

Initiating Pro-Active Budget, Advocacy, Educational,
and Corporate Energy Management Actions


Guest Speaker

Theo Johnson
 Manager, Best Practices Program
U.S. DOE, Office of Industrial Technologies

Task Force Scope, Issues and Strategies, and Mechanics

*	Education of media and policymakers on the benefits of industrial
energy-efficiency policies
*	Advocacy in support of restoration/increase in the Office of
Industrial Technologies (OIT) budget
*	Promotion of best corporate energy management practices by industry


